msgstr "HEIC और HEIF तस्वीरों को ऑनलाइन JPG, PNG या PDF में बदलें"

msgid ""
"<p><strong>HEIC to JPG</strong> conversion turns the High-Efficiency Image "
"Container files that iPhones and iPads create by default into formats every "
